data.description: Best buy currently in the Sand Springs area. What a fabulous floor plan ! No HOA is this small cul-de-sac neighborhood. Just down the road from local elementary school. Makes it super convenient. This one has all the extras already for you. Well loved and cared for, extra large home. Over 3000 sq ft and 4 or 5 bedrooms! 3 full baths. So many options for you to choose from. This beauty has 3 bedrooms down. One could be an office, split bedrooms down, so that everyone has their own space. Heated and cooled sunroom for your pets/plants, fully tiled with a ceiling fan too. Newer Cherry trees planted in the backyard, will be yielding some crops in the future. Move into this home with confidence. New heat and air, hot water heater, roof, dishwasher. Fresh paint, so clean and well cared for. oversized living space makes it a wonderful home for entertaining. Flex room up could be a theater room, was being used as an exercise room. Plenty of parking available in the driveway and garage. Full 3 car parking. Come see what this home has to offer! It is move in ready and all it needs is you!
